### About me
I'm currently a freshman studying computer engineering at the Unviversity at Buffalo. 

### Extra Curriculars
I've participated in a wide variety of activities at UB.  Within the past few months I've taken part in UB hacking as well as performed in a play with the Filipino American Student Association (FASA).
